h2. About

TestOOB is an advanced unit testing framework for Python. It integrates
effortlessly with existing PyUnit (module 'unittest') test suites.

!images/screenshot02.png(Screenshot)!

h2. Requirements

* Python 2.2 or higher
* "4Suite":http://4suite.org for HTML output.
* "Twisted":http://twistedmatrix.com/products/download for running in threads.

